@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Kelola Profil & Logout

actor User
boundary UI
control Controller
entity Database

User -> UI : Buka halaman Profil
UI -> Controller : Request data profil
Controller -> Database : SELECT * FROM User WHERE user_id = ?
Database --> Controller : Data profil
Controller --> UI : Tampilkan profil

User -> UI : Ubah data profil (nama, foto, cover)
UI -> Controller : Kirim perubahan
Controller -> Database : UPDATE User SET ...
Database --> Controller : OK
Controller --> UI : Notifikasi "Profil berhasil diperbarui"

User -> UI : Klik Logout
UI -> Controller : Request logout
Controller -> Database : UPDATE Session SET status='logout'
Database --> Controller : OK
Controller --> UI : Redirect ke halaman login

@enduml